nodes.text: Sennegrin Coops was a Human male individual who served the Sith Empire during the Galactic War.

Senneegrin Coops and Treezl Zillyons were originally part of a cut series of Star Wars: The Old Republic missions on the planet Balmorra that would have dealt with transferring supplies and Coops's corruption. Like several missions in Sobrik, the mission was cut before the game was launched, though Coops remained in the game.
